main event: A balloon-like object with pulsating lights was observed by air military personnel in N. Luffenham, England on October 21, 1957.
interesting points: The object exhibited erratic behavior, making sharp and sudden changes in direction.
The object was tracked on radar by the military.
There have been eight other similar sightings in the same area around the same time.
The FBI is investigating the sighting.
sighted object: a balloon-like object with pulsating lights
